page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the Python SDK'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with the Python SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- Python 3.8 or later version.- The following Python libraries: os.- An Azure OpenAI Service resource with either the `gpt-35-turbo` or the `gpt-4` models deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.> [!div class="nextstepaction"]> I ran into an issue with the prerequisites.
